# Group Announcement

## Announcement [/api/cms/announcement/{id}/]

+ Parameters
    + id (number) 
    
+ Attributes (object)
    + id: 1 (number)
    + title: title
    + type: 1 (number)
    + top: 1 (number)
    + status: 1 (number)
    + content: content
    + attachment (array)
    + creator: creator
    + created_time: `1980-09-02 00:00:00`
    + updated_time: `1980-09-02 00:00:00`  
    
         
### Retrieve a Announcement [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (Announcement)
    
### Update a Announcement [PATCH]

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    
## All Announcements [/api/cms/announcement/{?limit,offset,search}]

+ Attributes
    + count: 1 (number)
    + results (array[Announcement])

### Retrieve all Announcements [GET]

+ Parameters
    + limit
    + offset
    + search

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (All Announcements)

